Template: nsia/password_verify
Type: password
Description: Enter Password Again:
 Re-enter the password of the initial user account. This password
 must match the previous password.

Template: nsia/password
Type: password
Description: Password (must be at least 8 characters long):
 Enter the password of the initial user account. This password must
 be at least 8 characters long. Make sure to remember the password
 so you an log into the web-interface.
 ${desc}

Template: nsia/complete
Type: note
Description: NSIA is running on port 8080 (http://127.0.0.1:8080)
 NSIA was successfully installed and enabled as a daemon. Open a
 web-browser to http://127.0.0.1:8080 in order to access NSIA.